Warranty
Useless stat that no one cares about.
\n\n
Note: Some manufacturers have a strong chance to void warranties if they
discover aftermarket modification. Simply remove aftermarket parts and replace
with factory parts to claim warranty.

Hyper drive
Used for faster than light travel.
Low power mode: used for interplanetary travel within the same solar system.
Overdrive mode: used to travel 100's of light years quickly.

Hyper relay
Creates a wormhole for fast travel.
